source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: scss/expression/binary-operator-spacing.scss
---

# Input

```scss
// Biome intentionally normalizes spaces around SCSS binary operators.
// Prettier preserves some tight forms because of parser token shapes.
$interpolation-left-tight: #{$width}/2px;
$interpolation-left-tight-after: #{$width}/ 2px;
$interpolation-right-tight: 2px/#{$width};
$interpolation-right-tight-before: 2px /#{$width};

$comparison-tight: 1>$width;
$comparison-tight-after: 1 >$width;
$comparison-tight-before: 1> $width;

@if 1>$width {
color:red;
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
// Biome intentionally normalizes spaces around SCSS binary operators.
// Prettier preserves some tight forms because of parser token shapes.
$interpolation-left-tight: #{$width} / 2px;
$interpolation-left-tight-after: #{$width} / 2px;
$interpolation-right-tight: 2px / #{$width};
$interpolation-right-tight-before: 2px / #{$width};

$comparison-tight: 1 > $width;
$comparison-tight-after: 1 > $width;
$comparison-tight-before: 1 > $width;

@if 1 > $width {
	color: red;
}

```
